                <i class="bi bi-facebook"></i> T√çCH H·ª¢P FANPAGE (FACEBOOK LOGIN)
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row mb-4">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <div class="alert alert-light border">
                            <strong>B∆∞·ªõc 1: C·∫•u h√¨nh Facebook App</strong> (L·∫•y t·∫°i <code>developers.facebook.com</code>)
                            <br><small class="text-muted">Callback URL c·ªßa b√°c l√†: <strong><%= appUrl %>/auth/facebook/callback</strong> (H√£y d√°n link n√†y v√†o ph·∫ßn "Valid OAuth Redirect URIs" tr√™n Facebook Developer)</small>
                        </div>
                        <form action="/admin/save-fb-config" method="POST" class="row g-2 align-items-end">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <label class="small fw-bold">App ID:</label>
                                <input type="text" name="appId" class="form-control" value="<%= fbConfig.appId %>" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <label class="small fw-bold">App Secret:</label>
